metadata.name: Hunting Time
metadata.description:
The lake froze. Boats could not go fishing. There is a stream nearby. The place where it meets the lake is still open. A dangerous hunt begins. It's time to hunt for the fisherman on the ice. The thickness of the ice is 20 cm. The ice can break at any time. Human vs Nature.
